# Dirty Simon

The project, codenamed "Dirty Simon", is an experimental exploration to assess the feasibility of implementing a [Polkadot client](https://spec.polkadot.network/id-polkadot-protocol) in Typescript.

Functionality:

- Loads the Kusama Wasm runtime and genesis state
- Executes a test block using `Core_execute_block`

To install dependencies:

```bash
bun install
```

To run:

```bash
bun start
```
